{"tid":1190212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"理性討論 警車停係路口係合理行為","createTime":"2019-06-07T07:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T08:55:16.000Z","uid":35199,"like":5,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b5b95e70a7d52c17652d22e5633698941f16c0","tid":1190212,"uid":35199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T07:59:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/2831986200175759?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkon9agroup%2Fpermalink%2F2831986200175759%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8utOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=739febb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/2831986200175759?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n唔討論係咪陰謀，邊個主使，淨係講條車cam片。<br />\n<br />\n00:20秒開始，口罩男準備出路口掉汽油彈(有起跑姿勢) 。 點知出早左/的士走得太慢，00:21走返轉頭果下應該係同警車內司機對望完，淆底掉頭走。又衰在佢右手攞樽，仲著住火，警車司機緊係閃燈停車想落去逗佢。一閃燈口罩男就慌，拎埋個樽上車走又唔係，就是9旦掉出去，然後上車逃走。"},{"pid":"3e4d8bf154640c1876d41c16d262ec34992d5544","tid":1190212,"uid":52299,"like":14,"dislike":15,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:01:09.000Z","msg":"呢到唔會有理性討論"},{"pid":"19e2215b324cf870b1adcf608c19f566a65b3ba7","tid":1190212,"uid":46042,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:03:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好明顯係夾埋 <br />\n警車無端端停喺嗰個位 跟住比訊號打燈 叫夾埋嗰條友掉地下 跟住唔係追條友 而係讓條路俾佢逃走</span>"},{"pid":"5d2bf38968dbf2b9673c6752288fda19288bbe23","tid":1190212,"uid":46042,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:06:58.000Z","msg":"樓主係5毛 警察派來散播謠言"},{"pid":"fac8350edcd044d27500e9d643754329fee070e6","tid":1190212,"uid":35199,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"19e2215b324cf870b1adcf608c19f566a65b3ba7","tid":1190212,"uid":46042,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:03:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好明顯係夾埋 <br />\n警車無端端停喺嗰個位 跟住比訊號打燈 叫夾埋嗰條友掉地下 跟住唔係追條友 而係讓條路俾佢逃走</span>"},"citedBy":1,"repl